Best Male Char Round 2 is up! Zardus and Dinobot tied, so they're the only 
candidates now, so vote for one of them!

Also, some of you might notice that I am an incompetent mouse aimer, and have 
accidently deleted the "Best RPGer" poll. I added it back on, so please 
revote. And sorry for any inconvenience.

I gotta say I'm surprized by alot of the results, but congratulations on 
anyone who won, and those who didn't!

So far, the results are:

Best Story Line Creator:            JP3884@....
Best Female Character:          Iron Raptor.
Best Arrival Sequence:              DeathScythe.
Best Departure/Death Sequence:  Hell Beast.
Best Love Story:                    Prowl and Iron Raptor.
Best Villian:                       Zardus.
Best Leader Overall:                Iron Raptor.



Good night everyone. C ya all tomorrow!
